    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡普地牢是一款以技能构筑为核心的动作类 Roguelite 游戏，  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你将通过装备技能来击败蜂拥而至的敌人。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>购买、组合并产生技能协同效果，打造属于你的独特战斗风格。  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>通过战略性的选择征服地牢，走向胜利！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>技能核心系统</strong>：在游戏中获得的技能会装备到“技能核心”中。每个技能核心最多可装备5个技能，并被分配到特定的按键。战斗中，按下指定按键时，核心中的技能会按顺序依次触发。例如，按下Q键时，会依次触发该核心中装备的第一个技能到最后一个技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/07b882a8179bdd30da01d7e2751cdde6.poster.avif?t=1768969258\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/07b882a8179bdd30da01d7e2751cdde6.webm?t=1768969258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/07b882a8179bdd30da01d7e2751cdde6.mp4?t=1768969258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>技能购买与定制</strong>：每通过一个关卡后，玩家可以在商店中购买新技能或修改现有技能。根据所装备的技能，战斗风格会完全不同，玩家可以打造自己独特的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/2d9c829b03075f2654dc78e5de469d6d.poster.avif?t=1768969258\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/2d9c829b03075f2654dc78e5de469d6d.webm?t=1768969258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/2d9c829b03075f2654dc78e5de469d6d.mp4?t=1768969258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>战斗与战略技能操作</strong>：每个技能都有独特的属性，可以施加各种状态异常效果。玩家需要根据技能的属性和状态效果制定策略以击败敌人，利用技能间的协同作用，获得战斗中的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/54964e9e3fe19a66ee3fcc15a7b2ef01.poster.avif?t=1768969258\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/54964e9e3fe19a66ee3fcc15a7b2ef01.webm?t=1768969258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139550/extras/54964e9e3fe19a66ee3fcc15a7b2ef01.mp4?t=1768969258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
